OL,3,CCouncil to debate 'transparency' in
OL,4,Casylum seeker accommodation
OL,6,FAn Extraordinary Council meeting will
OL,7,Fbe held in Wrexham after plans to
OL,8,Fhouse asylum seekers in an empty
OL,9,Fassisted living facility in
OL,10,FRhosllanerchrugog.
OL,12,FA motion will be debated by council
OL,13,Fmembers on February 6 about fairness
OL,14,Fand transparency in the system of
OL,15,Ftemporary accommodation for asylum
OL,16,Fseekers, overseen by the Home Office.
