OL,3,CCouncil to debate 'transparency' in
OL,4,Casylum seeker accommodation
OL,6,FEarlier this month around 500 people
OL,7,Fattended a meeting in the village to
OL,8,Fraise questions about the proposal.
OL,10,FWrexham Council are objecting to the
OL,11,Fproposal and are unhappy with the
OL,12,Fprocess of consulation, claiming
OL,13,Fcouncils can sometimes be given "as
OL,14,Flittle as five days" to respond to
OL,15,Fproposals.
OL,17,FIt said: "This severely restricts our
OL,18,Fability as a council to plan, assess
OL,19,Fimpacts and consult with local
OL,20,Fcouncillors and local people.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/7
