OL,3,CCouncil to debate 'transparency' in
OL,4,Casylum seeker accommodation
OL,6,F"This blatant lack of meaningful
OL,7,Fconsultation with councils undermines
OL,8,Fpartnership working, places additional
OL,9,Fpressure on already stretched local
OL,10,Fservices, including health, and risks
OL,11,Fnegative outcomes for communities.
OL,13,F"The way the Home Office is conducting
OL,14,Fitself is unacceptable, and there has
OL,15,Fto be a public outcry about this.
OL,17,F"Public sector organisations across
OL,18,Fthe UK are expected to subscribe to
OL,19,Fthe Nolan Principles, which include
OL,20,Fopenness and transparency.
