OL,6,F"As a result, we call on the Prime
OL,7,FMinister Sir Keir Starmer to
OL,8,Fintervene, and to help ensure the Home
OL,9,FOffice takes the appropriate steps to
OL,10,Fcreate a fair and transparent system
OL,11,Ffor everyone."
OL,13,FThe Home Office has previously said:
OL,14,F"We are furious at the level of
OL,15,Fillegal migrants and asylum hotels.
