OL,3,CCouncil to debate 'transparency' in
OL,4,Casylum seeker accommodation
OL,6,F"This government will close every
OL,7,Fasylum hotel. Work is well underway to
OL,8,Fmove asylum seekers into more suitable
OL,9,Faccommodation such as military bases,
OL,10,Fto ease pressure on communities across
OL,11,Fthe country.
OL,13,F"We are working closely with local
OL,14,Fauthorities, property partners and
OL,15,Facross-government so that we can
OL,16,Faccelerate delivery."
OL,18,FITV News has approached Clearsprings
OL,19,Ffor a statement. They have previously
OL,20,Fdeclined to comment on this case.
